verbose_text: Electrical cardioversion is benign because it only delivers a minimal amount of current to the fetus.4 Recent ACC/AHA/ESC guidelines for management of SVT list catheter ablation as a reasonable approach in pregnant patients with highly symptomatic, recurrent, drug-refractory SVT with efforts toward minimizing radiation exposure.
